OL,3,CNewcastle murder investigation: Three
OL,4,Ccharged after stabbing of 25-year-old
OL,6,FThree people have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following the death of a man in
OL,8,FNewcastle.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FShields Road in the Byker area, where
OL,12,Fa suspected assault had been reported
OL,13,Fshortly after 7:25pm on Tuesday (16
OL,14,FJune).
OL,16,FOfficers found 25-year-old Gino Robb
OL,17,Fwith serious injuries consistent with
OL,18,Fthose caused by a bladed weapon.
OL,20,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,21,Fbut died a short time later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
