OL,3,CNewcastle murder investigation: Three
OL,4,Ccharged after stabbing of 25-year-old
OL,6,FA murder investigation was launched by
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police's Major
OL,8,FInvestigation Team, which treated the
OL,9,Fdeath as homicide from the outset.
OL,11,FFollowing initial enquiries, two men
OL,12,Faged 22 and 24 and a 16-year-old boy
OL,13,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,14,FA separate 40-year-old man was also
OL,15,Farrested in the Walker area on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder. All
OL,17,Ffour were later released on bail
OL,18,Fpending further investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
