OL,3,CNewcastle murder investigation: Three
OL,4,Ccharged after stabbing of 25-year-old
OL,6,FPolice confirmed on 21 June that three
OL,7,Fpeople have now been charged with
OL,8,Fmurder - they are 33-year-old Jed
OL,9,FGrieve of Orpington Avenue, Walker,
OL,10,Falong with two boys aged 14 and 16,
OL,11,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons.
OL,13,FAll three remain in police custody and
OL,14,Fare due to appear before Newcastle
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 22 June.
OL,17,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark
OL,18,FAtherton from Northumbria Police said
OL,19,Fhis thoughts were with the victim's
OL,20,Ffamily following what he described as
OL,21,Fa "tragic" incident.
