OL,3,CNewcastle murder investigation: Three
OL,4,Ccharged after stabbing of 25-year-old
OL,6,FHe added that officers are continuing
OL,7,Fto support the family and have asked
OL,8,Fthe public to respect their privacy
OL,9,Fduring what he acknowledged is a
OL,10,Fdeeply difficult time.
OL,12,FInvestigators remain active in the
OL,13,FByker and Walker areas, and are
OL,14,Fcarrying out further enquiries and
OL,15,Freassurance patrols.
