OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1782251281
OL,3,CNewcastle murder investigation: Three
OL,4,Ccharged after stabbing of 25-year-old
OL,6,FAs part of the ongoing investigation,
OL,7,Fpolice are asking for information
OL,8,Fabout two people seen on an electric
OL,9,Fmotorbike believed to have entered
OL,10,FShields Road from the Grace Street
OL,11,Farea shortly before the incident,
OL,12,Fbefore leaving back in the same
OL,13,Fdirection.
OL,15,FOfficers are also appealing for any
OL,16,FCCTV, dashcam, or mobile phone footage
OL,17,Ffrom the surrounding area at around
OL,18,Fthe time of the attack.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
